        "boundary": "The ADR specifies that certain SASS import syntaxes are deprecated. All SASS files need to be reviewed (or linted) to conform to the new import style before the builder can process them successfully.",
        "severity": "caution",
        "source_facts": [
          "ADR: UVZ-09-ADR-003 Frontend Build Strategy SASS Import Deprecation"
        ]
