        "answer": "The patch was created for Angular 18. You must locate the patch files (likely under `patches/ng-bootstrap`) and verify whether they still apply cleanly to the ng‑bootstrap version compatible with Angular 19. If not, the patch will need to be updated or the upstream library upgraded to a version that already includes the fix."
      },
